      <title>捷克总理罢免部长引发联盟政府动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/czech-premier-moves-to-oust-of-junior-party-leader-from-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克总理彼得·菲亚拉（Petr Fiala）更换了来自小执政党的一名部长，导致其越来越不受欢迎的联合政府在大选前一年陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/czech-premier-moves-to-oust-of-junior-party-leader-from-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 11:29:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
